<h4><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2020/09/06/ipad-and-watch-press-release-september-8/">苹果或于本周发布新 iPad 和 Apple Watch</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1363678" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPad-and-watch-soon-2.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="450" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPad-and-watch-soon-2.jpg 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPad-and-watch-soon-2-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPad-and-watch-soon-2-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>MacRumors 消息，爆料者 Jon Prosser 称苹果正准备于 9 月 8 日的新闻发布，根据此前消息，这次发布应该会带来新的 Apple Watch 和 iPad。Jon Prosser 表示，这个日期仍未完全确定。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1363679" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/a-1.png" alt="" width="535" height="254" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/a-1.png 535w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/a-1-360x171.png 360w" sizes="(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px" /></p>
<p>与此同时，《彭博社》的 Mark Gurman 今天在 Twitter 上表示，他认为本周苹果不会发布新品，而是更有可能公布 9 月份苹果发布会这个消息本身。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1363680" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/d.png" alt="" width="536" height="233" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/d.png 536w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/d-360x156.png 360w" sizes="(max-width: 536px) 100vw, 536px" /></p>
<h4><a href="http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2020-09-06/1499670.html">我国可重复使用试验航天器发射后成功返回</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1363681" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/kunh.png" alt="" width="1200" height="864" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/kunh.png 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/kunh-360x259.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/kunh-768x553.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/kunh-1024x737.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>新华社消息，我国在酒泉卫星发射中心成功发射的可重复使用航天器，在轨飞行 2 天后，于 9 月 6 日成功返回预定着陆场。这次试验的圆满成功，标志着我国可重复使用航天器技术研究取得重要突破，后续可为和平利用太空提供更加便捷、廉价的往返方式。</p>
